rows.label: qev058803_MSG0001
rows.name:
Noborata and Tikotiko spend every day lying about.
Never look for work. Ugh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev058803_MSG0002
rows.name:
...Me? I come to plaza every day. Chat to learn of
people from other planets. You have problem with this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev058803_MSG0003
rows.name:
...Sorry. I am busy. I am teaching Orphean here about
taming beasts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev058803_MSG0004
rows.name:
Though I am not sure it can be done by one so...
bug-like? Food-like?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev058803_MSG0005
rows.name: Prone could tame beast that size without fail.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev058803_MSG0006
rows.name:
But this one? We will not know until he tries.
He is determined, but also bit...bug-like? Food-like?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev058803_MSG0007
rows.name:
Will Min'barac be all right? I worry about him going
near beasts. He is bit...food-like himself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev058803_MSG0008
rows.name: Maybe we should check on him later.[ST:wait ]
